  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "chapterTitle": "第12章 销售会谈的四个阶段",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300130156_18_7388-7445",
          "range": "7388-7445",
          "rangeStart": 7388,
          "rangeEnd": 7445,
          "markText": "如果销售会谈的结果不能达成使生意向前推进的一致（即暂时中断），那么就是不成功的，不论买方看起来多么愉快、多么满意。",
          "colorStyle": 2,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1774421063,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2026-03-25 14:44:23",
          "chapterUid": 18,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300130156&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=7388&rangeEnd=7445",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fea329b0813ab9957g0166d2?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=7388&rangeEnd=7445"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300130156_5_4679-4716",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "4679-4716",
      "markText": "例如，先弄清异议产生的原因，然后用一种可以想到的方式对原来的说法变更一下。",
      "totalCount": 2710,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300130156&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4679&rangeEnd=4716",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fea329b0813ab9957g0166d2?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4679&rangeEnd=4716"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300130156_12_11396-11451",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "11396-11451",
      "markText": "绝大多数销售人员都承认会谈计划的重要性，但在现实中，他们自己计划的重要性只不过是会谈开始前的片刻惶惶不安而已。",
      "totalCount": 2701,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300130156&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=11396&rangeEnd=11451",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fea329b0813ab9957g0166d2?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=11396&rangeEnd=11451"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300130156_5_16879-16917",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "16879-16917",
      "markText": "尽管它对某种类型的客户来说有一定的效果，比如那些很爱唠叨总是说个不停的客户。",
      "totalCount": 2622,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300130156&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=16879&rangeEnd=16917",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fea329b0813ab9957g0166d2?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=16879&rangeEnd=16917"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300130156_24_14375-14412",
      "chapterUid": 24,
      "range": "14375-14412",
      "markText": "如果你不必花时间来处理A/V员工的难题，那么对你的其他管理职责会有何帮助？",
      "totalCount": 2608,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300130156&chapterUid=24&rangeStart=14375&rangeEnd=14412",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fea329b0813ab9957g0166d2?chapterUid=24&rangeStart=14375&rangeEnd=14412"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300130156_6_4246-4363",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "4246-4363",
      "markText": "现在我已经意识到了，对我而言，销售并不仅仅是一种学术上的研究，还必须使我的这些研究成果作为一项服务方式销售出去，否则我就会饿死，也就是说对销售的研究已经成为我生存的需要了，因此，我组织了一项销售培训课程，而且特别注意收场白技巧的应用。",
      "totalCount": 2589,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300130156&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=4246&rangeEnd=4363",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fea329b0813ab9957g0166d2?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=4246&rangeEnd=4363"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300130156_23_11082-11126",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "11082-11126",
      "markText": "卖方最经常犯而且最危险的一个错误就是在明确需求被完全开发之前介绍自己的对策（解决方案）。",
      "totalCount": 2580,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300130156&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=11082&rangeEnd=11126",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fea329b0813ab9957g0166d2?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=11082&rangeEnd=11126"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300130156_6_36014-36066",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "36014-36066",
      "markText": "大订单销售中一次会谈可能需要几个小时，所涉话题很宽泛，客户对于每一个讨论的问题并不一定都有很详细的了解。",
      "totalCount": 2524,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300130156&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=36014&rangeEnd=36066",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fea329b0813ab9957g0166d2?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=36014&rangeEnd=36066"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300130156_16_4257-4295",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "4257-4295",
      "markText": "做好你的准备工作，最好是从其他来源和地位比较低的人那里收集与事实有关的信息。",
      "totalCount": 2511,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300130156&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=4257&rangeEnd=4295",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fea329b0813ab9957g0166d2?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=4257&rangeEnd=4295"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300130156_12_7715-7759",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "7715-7759",
      "markText": "我们的研究表明，传统的开放型提问和封闭型提问之间的区别并不能预示着在大订单销售中的成功。",
      "totalCount": 2506,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300130156&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=7715&rangeEnd=7759",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fea329b0813ab9957g0166d2?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=7715&rangeEnd=7759"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300130156_22_5858-5908",
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "range": "5858-5908",
      "markText": "■ 销售周期的初期——在你收集到足够的背景信息来做一个计划及取得了买方的信任之后，可以讨论客户难题。",
      "totalCount": 2497,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300130156&chapterUid=22&rangeStart=5858&rangeEnd=5908",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fea329b0813ab9957g0166d2?chapterUid=22&rangeStart=5858&rangeEnd=5908"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300130156_24_15429-15463",
      "chapterUid": 24,
